      "date": "2012-12-19 17:27:29.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Looks good to me, approved\n\nIs this patch from upstream?  If yes, then the commit comment should include the commit hash for the upstream kernel patch. If not, is there a patch needed to fix the same problem in the upstream kernel?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
